This is a clone of FFmpeg with some enhancements on HTTP live streaming

- Each variant belongs to a program. This avoids issue of fetching two separate
variants for video and audio respectively.
- Follow http redirection for manifest file. This is needed for some Live Streaming

FFmpeg README
-------------

1) Documentation
----------------

* Read the documentation in the doc/ directory in git.
  You can also view it online at http://ffmpeg.org/documentation.html

2) Licensing
